Introduction

Future versions of the WebTV Internet receiver will be based upon the
Microsoft Windows CE operating system. This provides a golden opportunity
for third-party game developers. They can develop games using Windows CE and
deliver them to a large audience. This has many advantages:

   * The game can be developed using the Microsoft Visual Studio development
     tools.
   * The developer can leverage their existing knowledge of the Microsoft
     Win32 API.
   * The developer can reuse code developed for other Microsoft Win32 and
     Microsoft Windows CE platforms.

